  "texts": [
    "Factors such as model comprehensiveness, accuracy, and potential sources of interference should be considered.",
    "Clinical judgment, rooted in experience, should guide decision-making.",
    "Continuous monitoring and performance optimization are crucial.",
    "LLMs offer promise as diagnostic aids, but healthcare professionals must weigh multiple factors to ensure the delivery of precise and thorough diagnostic recommendations to patients.",
    "Our study shifted focus to MediGuide-14B, our proprietary open-source model."
